29#ifndef _PRIVATE_RIJNDAEL_H
30#define _PRIVATE_RIJNDAEL_H
31
32#define AES_MAXKEYBITS (256)
33#define AES_MAXKEYBYTES (AES_MAXKEYBITS/8)
34/* for 256-bit keys, fewer for less */
35#define AES_MAXROUNDS 14
36
37typedef unsigned char u8;
38typedef unsigned short u16;
39typedef unsigned int u32;
40
41int rijndaelKeySetupEnc(unsigned int [], const unsigned char [], int);
42void rijndaelEncrypt(const unsigned int [], int, const unsigned char [],
43 unsigned char []);
44
45#endif /* _PRIVATE_RIJNDAEL_H */
